ts on sale graphic" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. - The West Virginia University baseball team has earned the No. 16 overall seed in the 2026 NCAA Baseball Championship and will host the NCAA Morgantown Regional at Kendrick Family Ballpark this Friday, May 29 through Monday, June 1.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg"><media:title>Regional Tickets on sale graphic</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 14:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59137</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Set for NCAA East First Round</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/track-field-mountaineers-set-for-ncaa-east-first-round</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/track-field-mountaineers-set-for-ncaa-east-first-round</guid><category>Track &amp; Field</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Mercy Kinyanjui competing at the Big 12 Outdoor Track and Field Championships" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University track and field team travels to Lexington, Kentucky, for the 2026 NCAA East First Round.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg"><media:title>Mercy Kinyanjui competing at the Big 12 Outdoor Track and Field Championships</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 12:21:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>16</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59138</s:story_id></item><item><title>Parking Information for NCAA Morgantown Regional</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/baseball-parking-information-for-ncaa-morgantown-regional</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/baseball-parking-information-for-ncaa-morgantown-regional</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="An overhead shot of Kendrick Family Ballpark during a West Virginia baseball game" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/27/RMB_2994.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. - The West Virginia University baseball team will open NCAA Regional play against Binghamton on Friday, May 29, at 5 p.m. ET, on ESPN+, while Wake Forest and Kentucky will meet in Friday's first game, at 12 p.m. ET on ESPN2. The Morgantown Regional will continue with games at 12 p.m. and 5 p.m. on Saturday and Sunday, with Monday's game time being released later this week if necessary.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/RMB_2994.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/image